# Available Scripts

All scripts should be run using `pnpm`. The following scripts are available:

## Core Scripts
- `pnpm start`: Run the main application
- `pnpm lint`: Run ESLint on the codebase

## Data Processing Scripts
- `pnpm create-profiles`: Create organization profiles by state
- `pnpm search-orgs`: Perform Google searches for organizations
- `pnpm crawl-sites`: Parse search results
- `pnpm chat`: Run the chat script

## Batch Processing
- `pnpm generate-batch-confirmation-file`: Generate batch confirmation file
- `pnpm parse-batch-responses`: Parse batch responses
- `pnpm confirm-with-local`: Confirm with local data
